===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|madeleine|lang=fr}}, earlier {{term|lang=fr|gâteau à la Madeleine}}, of uncertain origin; attributed in some sources to a 19th-century pastry cook [[w:Madeleine Paulmier|Madeleine Paulmier]] whose existence is now considered dubious.  (Compare Oxford English Dictionary, ''Trésor de la Langue Française'')

